item.title: CVE-2021-21598|2024-09-17T04:25:09.114Z -- dell -- wyse%20thinos
item.description: Dell Wyse ThinOS, versions 9.0, 9.1, and 9.1 MR1, contain a Sensitive Information Disclosure Vulnerability. An authenticated attacker with physical access to the system could exploit this vulnerability to read sensitive Smartcard data in log files.
